This is a rust project  using workspace as central point. 

All dependencies definition is inside workspace Cargo.toml.

Crates  are inside crates directory except tools crate that is a crate with developement delpers.

Crates inside workspace uses dependencies for workspace defining it only with DEPENDENCY_NAME.workspace=true

important paths are defined in .cargo/config.toml

project uses cargo-make to make running commands inside workspace more convinient.

always save whole documentation for any crate workspace is using into markdown format to workspace folder docs/crates/crate_name

keep important facts and observations about crates and usage that might be used in the future in workspace folder docs/notes using name that show what those notes are about and markdown format
